Details

-Weakens sound-based moves by 50%

-Un-grounds all battlers so that they are immune to ground

-Boosts flying-type damage by 30%

-Boosts the power of 'Wind' moves (Razor Wind, Gust, Blizzard, Aeroblast, Powder Snow, Icy Wind, Air Cutter, Silver Wind, Air Slash, Ominous Wind, Hurricane, Glaciate, Fairy Wind, Wing Attack, Dual Wingbeat, Steel Wing, Oblivion Wing)
